column5: Anyone fishing the lower Ganaraska for rainbows? If so, what are the conditions? Open water? Ice?
completely blown out . the water is fast and dirty. if it freezes it may calm down they have been catching fish in the am.  if your on facebook do a search for ganaraskafishway
Thanks for the info.  I'll check out the facebook link.
I have no info but i will say this. I love the handle "Crazy Ivan".  Well done.  :-p
I seen some nice big Ice chunks floating down the river today..
